{"title":"将军不下马","authors":["池北偶"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":1,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军不下马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华君武画　池北偶诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上马的时节你争我抢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下马的时节我推你让。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甲说：“先人后己”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乙说：“计议从长”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丙说：“欲罢不能”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁说：“决不买账”……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的嘀嘀咕咕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的嘟嘟嚷嚷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的不声不响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的骂爹骂娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个使劲夹住马鞍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个抓紧缰绳不放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁可在马背上打盹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不愿脚踏实地奔忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诸君的阵地应当缩小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己的战线不妨拉长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"调整、改革让别人干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巩固、提高由我承当。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民需要什么，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全局利益怎样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道都不放在心上？"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}